name: Ángel Dior
description: '''Ángel Rosario''', known by his stage name '''Ángel Dior''', is a Dominican rapper and singer. Rosario was born in 2003, [[Santo Domingo]], [[Dominican Republic]]. He was awarded in the [[Heat Latin Music Awards]] and [[Premios Juventud]] in the categories; Best Dominican Urban Artist, and Best Dembow Collaboration. He has collaborated with [[Rauw Alejandro]], [[Karol G]], [[6ix9ine]], [[El Alfa]], [[Chimbala]] and [[Bad Bunny]].
